# Docker: platform amd64

Production server is **linux/amd64**. Development may be Mac arm64.

## Required

- `docker build` must include `--platform linux/amd64`
- Compose build/run must declare `platform: linux/amd64`
- Never publish an arm64-only image to Docker Hub for this project

## Correct

```bash
docker build --platform linux/amd64 -t ingluigii/btw-template-pdf:latest .
docker push ingluigii/btw-template-pdf:latest
```

## Incorrect

```bash
docker build -t ingluigii/btw-template-pdf:latest .
```
